        "action": "Change law to require employers to offer flexible working to menopausal women",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "The symptoms of the menopause can be very disabling for many women which can go on for years and having to work set hours can make it even harder, which I and others have experienced. Let's get it out in the open and make life easier for women, which will also make life better for all in the future",
